Luxor By Imtiaz - Where Luxury Meets Sophistication

Uploaded: 7 months ago

Luxor By Imtiaz - Where Luxury Meets Sophistication

Discover the newest addition in the heart of JVC, Luxor by Imtiaz Developments in Dubai. This remarkable 35-story project offers luxurious studios and 1–2 bedroom apartments, ensuring unparalleled comfort for its residents. With a stylish architectural design, this project provides residents with a modern and aesthetically pleasing living space.

 

Indulge in the ultimate luxury living experience at Luxor by Imtiaz Developments. The exquisite apartment tower has a lavish swimming pool, a modern gym, and a picturesque sky garden. The residences' elegant finishings and opulent interiors exude refinement and grace, making it a distinguished address for those seeking an upscale lifestyle. All apartments have Alexa smart home technology, a 65-inch smart TV, premium Italian tiles, and exquisite sanitary ware. Here is your opportunity to explore a lifestyle like never before. Enjoy breathtaking views of the Dubai skyline and other attractive sights. As a leading property developer in Dubai, Imtiaz Developments provides flexible payment plans to suit buyers, including a 60/40 payment plan.

 

Luxor by Imtiaz is strategically located within Jumeirah Village Circle (JVC), providing residents with effortless access to significant areas, commercial districts, shopping centers, hospitals, and schools. It is also close to the Circle Mall, Dubai Butterfly Garden, Mall of the Emirates, Burj Al Arab, and other popular destinations like Dubai Marina, Palm Jumeirah, Downtown Dubai, Business Bay, and Dubai International Airport.
